Question: Write a summary (plot synopsis) of your favorite movie.
Answer:
My favorite movie would have to be The Mask. In the movie, a down-on-his-luck bank clerk named Stanley Ipkiss happens upon a magical mask that transforms a person into their innermost desires. In Stanley's case, it transforms into a cartoon character that loves mischief but it can be dangerous weapon in the hands of people with darker desires as Stanley soon learns. Its then up to Stanley and his dog Max to save the city.